            opens his tournament, our town gets hit
            with an avalanche of garbage blocks!
            
            It'll be a while before we can clean
            it all up. Sorry, kiddo.")
    release
}

script WaddleDeeTown_EventScript_WorkerRight
{
    lock
    faceplayer
    msgbox("Supposedly the Great King gave out an
            order to restrict the town's north exit.
            
            But when he saw all these blockades, he
            cried out, \qothis is way too far!\qc
            
            Does he think we're the ones who
            caused this mess\.?")
    release
}

